import React from 'react'
import {FooterContainer,FooterWrapper,FooterLinksContainer, FooterLinkItems,
    FooterLinksWrapper,FooterLinkTitle,FooterLink,SocialLogo,
    SocialMediaWrapper,WebsiteRights,SocialIconLink,SocialIcons} from './FooterComponents'
import {FaGithub,FaFacebook, FaInstagram, FaLinkedin} from 'react-icons/fa'

const Footer = () => {
    return (
        <FooterContainer>
        <FooterWrapper>
        <FooterLinksContainer>
        <FooterLinksWrapper>
        <FooterLinkItems>
        <FooterLinkTitle>Social Media </FooterLinkTitle>
        <FooterLink to ="//www.linkedin.com/in/shraddhabelbase/" target="_blank">LinkedIN</FooterLink>
        <FooterLink to ="//www.facebook.com/shraddha.belbase" target="_blank">Facebook</FooterLink>
        <FooterLink to="//www.facebook.com/" target="_blank">Instagram</FooterLink>
        <FooterLink to="//twitter.com/shraaddhhaa" target="_blank">Twitter</FooterLink>
        </FooterLinkItems>
        <FooterLinkItems>
        <FooterLinkTitle>Projects </FooterLinkTitle>
        <FooterLink to ="//github.com/shraddhabelbase/Greenfoot" target="_blank">SpiderGame</FooterLink>
        <FooterLink to ="//github.com/shraddhabelbase/Website-Coffee-Shop-" target="_blank">Coffee</FooterLink>
        <FooterLink to ="//github.com/shraddhabelbase/katy_trail_app" target="_blank">Katy-Trail-App</FooterLink>
        <FooterLink to ="//github.com/shraddhabelbase/Teacher-Dashboard-To-do-List-" target="_blank">Website</FooterLink>
        </FooterLinkItems>
        </FooterLinksWrapper>
        <FooterLinksWrapper>
        <FooterLinkItems>
        <FooterLinkTitle>Hackathons </FooterLinkTitle>
        <FooterLink to ="/">PickHacks</FooterLink>
        <FooterLink to ="/">TigerHacks</FooterLink>
        <FooterLink to ="/">UMSLHacks</FooterLink>
        <FooterLink to ="/"></FooterLink>
        </FooterLinkItems>
        <FooterLinkItems>
        <FooterLinkTitle>Blog Posts </FooterLinkTitle>
        <FooterLink to="//www.techitlikethat.wordpress.com/2019/09/19/23/" target="_blank">Github</FooterLink>
        <FooterLink to ="/">Wordpress</FooterLink>
        <FooterLink to="//www.techitlikethat.wordpress.com/2019/01/09/mac-tips-for-windows-users/" target="_blank">Mac Tips</FooterLink>
        <FooterLink to="//www.techitlikethat.wordpress.com/2020/01/19/getting-started-with-r/" target="_blank">R-Script</FooterLink>
        </FooterLinkItems>
        </FooterLinksWrapper></FooterLinksContainer>
        <SocialMediaWrapper>
        <SocialLogo to ='/'>
        </SocialLogo>
        {/*<WebsiteRights>©{new Date().getFullYear()}</WebsiteRights>*/}
        <SocialIcons>
        <SocialIconLink href="//www.github.com/shraddhabelbase" target="_blank" area_label="Github"><FaGithub/></SocialIconLink>
        <SocialIconLink href="//www.facebook.com/shraddha.belbase" target="_blank" area_label="Facebook"><FaFacebook/></SocialIconLink>
   
        <SocialIconLink href="//www.instagram.com/__shraddhaaa__/" target="_blank" area_label="Instagram"><FaInstagram/></SocialIconLink>
   
        <SocialIconLink href="//www.linkedin.com/in/shraddhabelbase/" target="_blank" area_label="LinkedIN"><FaLinkedin/></SocialIconLink></SocialIcons>
        </SocialMediaWrapper></FooterWrapper>
        </FooterContainer>
    )
}

export default Footer
